name: Malu Hanat
description:
A satirical piece on Malaysian political shenanigans.

Weathered-gold-painted sculpture covering Tunku Abdul Rahman statue with "Pantun" (a Malayan form of repetitive poetry). 

Parlimen bergema suara,
Caci maki menunjuk belang
Parlimen bergema suara,
Berpanjikan babi, beruk dan f**k you
menutup belang.

And a scrolling text that says "May God save you". ​
